I love the fact that yoga is so ancient. With all of the knowledge we have and technological advancements, science still doesn‚Äôt understand how the ancients were right about so many things, especially healing the body, mind, and spirit naturally. Yoga practice gives me a place to put down my roots while I‚Äôm busy trying to grow my branches. 

I‚Äôve slowly developed space, self-care and healing, regularity in my physical body, and reversal of a disorder that would‚Äôve been life changing had it progressed. I honestly can‚Äôt wait for my next physical in a few weeks so I can tell my Dr. exactly what changes I‚Äôve made in order to achieve all of the goals she set for me. I‚Äôm not down to my exact goal weight yet, but I‚Äôm getting there in a healthy way, slow and steady, and with pure enjoyment. Yoga is a HUGE part of that. 

Adriene, I don‚Äôt think we could thank you enough for making yoga accessible to us like this.
